Veteran Nollywood actress and ordained preacher, Eucharia Anunobi, has advised couples intending to marry not to settle down with their partner if he or she is boring. The cleric disclosed this on Wednesday via her verified Instagram page, stating that settling for a boring partner would be a disservice to oneself and the other person. She wrote, “If you find him or her boring, don’t settle for them. That will be a disservice to yourself and that other person. -Advertisement- “YOU ARE TO LIVE LIFE ABUNDANTLY NOT LIVING A CONTRIVED LIFE. John 10:10.”